        public void setTag(java.lang.String name,
          java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.SortedSet<EID>> collection)
        Set the tag with the provided set of events. When an existing tag is again set, the instances could be changed. Therefore we disable any currently enabled tag instances for the provided tag name.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the tag. (Cannot be 'null' or an empty string)
        collection - Collection of instances of events (EIDs)
